---
title: Herbed Chicken & Chickpea Spinach Salad with Apple, Feta, Almonds & Italian Dressing
description: We’re putting a new spin on spinach salad—and this hearty supper stunner is ready for a twirl. Crisped-up herby chickpeas, toasted almonds, and briny-tangy feta cheese are balanced by a sweet and tart cherry balsamic dressing, and juicy bites of pear to make a light yet satisfying meal. We’ll have you whirling for joy when dinner’s ready in 30 minutes.
